77
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:38,080
Go ahead with your busy schedule.

78
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:39,260
I really don't need that.

79
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:42,920
But I think that's a good idea.

80
00:03:42,920 --> 00:03:44,120
You see, with your temper,

81
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,680
I'm worried something might go wrong.

82
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:47,240
What's more, it's safer for you

83
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:48,380
to have a guy with you.

84
00:03:49,640 --> 00:03:50,480
Mr. Shu,

85
00:03:50,480 --> 00:03:51,640
