Wait, Mr. Shu.

101
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:21,900
Will I get paid for these days off, Meng?

102
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:24,120
For the company,

103
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:26,220
I'll work online until I get back.

104
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:30,860
Mr. Shu, are you really going there?

105
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:32,460
