106
00:04:32,760 --> 00:04:33,600
No.

107
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:35,840
But remember to check
your phone messages.

108
00:04:35,840 --> 00:04:37,000
Otherwise, if something happens to you,

109
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,500
- Fine.
- I can't handle it.

110
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:41,440
