113
00:04:46,160 --> 00:04:47,000
- Go back.
- Go.

114
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:48,150
- I'll be fine.
- Okay, bye.

115
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:54,040
Enjoy the ride.

116
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:56,340
