185
00:08:30,400 --> 00:08:31,420
But didn't you...

186
00:08:33,680 --> 00:08:35,300
- Assistant Lin.
- Hello.

187
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:42,360
But didn't you say

188
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:44,800
