200
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:24,820
Mr. Shu has other work today.

201
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:26,820
He will join us online.

202
00:09:28,800 --> 00:09:29,980
Online? Again?

203
00:09:30,150 --> 00:09:31,850
