214
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:04,700
What should we do?

215
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:07,020
Let's go back. The car is still there.

216
00:10:07,560 --> 00:10:08,420
Wait.

217
00:10:09,040 --> 00:10:11,100
