220
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:17,680
Sir,

221
00:10:17,800 --> 00:10:20,460
do you know where Organic Milk Farm is?

222
00:10:21,280 --> 00:10:23,140
It's up ahead, about 2.5 kilometers away.

223
00:10:24,680 --> 00:10:25,520
Let's go.

224
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:28,300
It's 2.5 kilometers away.

225
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:29,500
