238
00:11:19,620 --> 00:11:20,600
Alright, no more waiting.

239
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:21,680
Let's begin.

240
00:11:22,600 --> 00:11:23,800
As for the Food Street,

241
00:11:23,800 --> 00:11:24,920
our operations department

242
00:11:24,920 --> 00:11:27,680
