264
00:12:41,520 --> 00:12:42,820
Mr. Shu is here.

265
00:12:42,960 --> 00:12:44,020
Mr. Shu is here.

266
00:12:46,040 --> 00:12:46,940
Sorry,

267
00:12:47,160 --> 00:12:48,480
