274
00:13:00,840 --> 00:13:02,340
Did you go to Hua Su again?

275
00:13:02,560 --> 00:13:03,400
No,

276
00:13:04,040 --> 00:13:05,420
I'm inspecting the food.

277
00:13:06,520 --> 00:13:07,680
